title: Cliff Martinez - Only God Forgives + You're My Dream edit
description:
The Only God Forgives soundtrack, plus a different edit of You're My Dream that I made.  It's just a touch longer.  I liked the way the song ended in the first trailer, and was disappointed by the album version's ending.  I did a little clipping and chopping and I'm happier with the edit, as are all my friends.  Hope you enjoy it!  If not, the original is still there.
Comment on what you think.
